OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,FLiverpool manager Arne Slot has
OL,7,Fexpressed his surprise that the
OL,8,FHillsborough Law has still not been
OL,9,Fimplemented, as the club prepares to
OL,10,Fmark 37 years since the disaster that
OL,11,Fclaimed the lives of 97 fans.
OL,13,FWriting in the matchday programme for
OL,14,FLiverpool's Champions League fixture
OL,15,Fagainst Paris Saint-Germain on
OL,16,FTuesday, 14 April, Slot paid a
OL,17,Fheartfelt tribute to the victims,
OL,18,Fsurvivors, and the bereaved families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
