PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,FSince taking over as head coach, Slot
OL,7,Frevealed he has spent time learning
OL,8,Fabout the 1989 tragedy, stating that
OL,9,Fthe "passage of time does not make
OL,10,F(the stories) any less moving."
OL,12,FThe Dutchman backed the campaign for a
OL,13,FHillsborough Law, which would legally
OL,14,Frequire public officials to tell the
OL,15,Ftruth during inquiries and
OL,16,Finvestigations.
OL,26,@rD@ApmrD@Mpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,F"I have also been told about the
OL,7,Fcampaign for a Hillsborough Law and
OL,8,Fhaving listened to the reasons and
OL,9,Fknowing the story behind them, it
OL,10,Fsurprises me that this is still to be
OL,11,Fintroduced," Slot wrote.
OL,13,FHe emphasised that his support for the
OL,14,Flegislation transcends his role at
OL,15,FAnfield: "This is not an opinion based
OL,16,Fon my association with Liverpool FC
OL,17,Feither.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,F"It is the view of someone who
OL,7,Fbelieves bereaved families should not
OL,8,Fhave to fight and campaign for the
OL,9,Ftruth about how their loved ones lost
OL,10,Ftheir lives, it should be provided as
OL,11,Fa matter of course."
OL,13,FWednesday, 15 April, marks 37 years
OL,14,Fsince the disaster.
OL,16,FLabour pledged to introduce a
OL,17,FHillsborough Law in its 2024
OL,18,Fmanifesto, but the legislation `
OL,19,Fformally known as the Public Office
OL,20,F(Accountability) Bill ` has stalled
OL,21,Fsince it was introduced in September.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
