PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,FIn 2025, the Government faced a row
OL,7,Fafter proposing amendments that would
OL,8,Fsee spies brought within the scope of
OL,9,Fthe law, but only with the approval of
OL,10,Fthe head of their services.
OL,12,FCampaigners warned that this could be
OL,13,Fused as a way of escaping the new
OL,14,F"duty of candour" and the amendments
OL,15,Fwere pulled, with reports now
OL,16,Fsuggesting intelligence chiefs will
OL,17,Fhave to make a court application for
OL,18,Fany disclosures to be exempted.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
