FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,FAsked about the Bill on Monday, Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer reiterated his commitment
OL,8,Fto deliver on his promise to introduce
OL,9,Fa Hillsborough Law.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister said: "Obviously
OL,12,Fwe're working with the families and
OL,13,Fothers on the final balance that we
OL,14,Fneed to get right in the proposed
OL,15,Flegislation.
OL,17,F"But the duty of candour, the duty,
OL,18,Fbasically, that public officials need
OL,19,Fto come forward and tell the truth `
OL,20,Fthat's a really important principle
OL,21,Fthat drives me.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776280294
OL,3,CSlot 'surprised' Hillsborough Law not
OL,4,Cyet introduced
OL,6,F"So, we'll keep working on this, it's
OL,7,Fimportant to get it right... I've made
OL,8,Fa promise and I intend to act on that
OL,9,Fpromise."
OL,11,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,12,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,13,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,14,Four region.
